(1, 'leave', 'leave', '离开，遗忘；保持一定状态；留下 (v.)', 'v.', '/liːv/', '{"meaning":"离开，遗忘；保持一定状态；留下 (v.)","examples":["My baby gets upset when I leave the room. — 我一离开房间宝宝就会不安。","Before leaving the train, make sure you have all your belongings with you. — 下火车前一定要带好随身物品。","Leave the motorway at Junction 7. — 请在七号交叉路口驶离高速公路。"],"etymology":null}', 3001),
